Ashby Cottage is a perfect getaway for that romantic weekend away from prying eye's or will accommodate for a night away with friends,the choice is your's!

Situated high on the hill at Ashby with beautiful views of the Clarence River,coastal plains extending  to the ocean. The cottage has it's own large private balcony with barbecue ,two bedrooms,two bathrooms,(one with spa),make your own cocktails in your self contained kitchen,while your guests wait in the dining room or lounge with a rustic wood fireplace,With all the mod cons such as  TV, DVD, VCR, CD and  for those hot day's the swimming pool will keep you cool as your car sits pretty in it's own carport.
Wake up to the serenity of silence as the surrounding nature starts the day with you. Enjoy cooking your own breakfast the way you like it provided by us. Be at peace as you gaze over the magnificent Clarence valley and beyond,feel the city stress slip away. So just give us a call we're already here.

column2: Aunty Marls Dog Friendly Holiday Cottage
column22:
Feel like getting away but don't want to leave your beloved pooch with friend's or family. Well don't,bring them along they'll love it. Yamba has it's own dog friendly beach where the tree's meet the sea, they can chase all the seagulls they want.
The cottage is well cleaned after every visitor. Your best mate can hang out with you inside as the cottage is fully tiled. If you feel like going out for lunch without your mate, they'll be alright hanging out in the fully fenced backyard. I thought I should mention that Yamba is human friendly also, so come check it out.

This Motel is situated within walking distance of Yamba's main street where you can find just about anything your after, including Yamba Bowling Club directly opposite. If you don't feel like going  out, just lay back in your Air-conditioned room or choose one our activities such as Wireless internet, Austar or have a barbeque overlooking our tropical pool. If you want to treat yourself ask about our Ocean view Apartment.

Scorpio Holiday Units are among Yamba's exclusive Ocean st. With spacious two bedroom units and Northeast facing balconies, kick back with all the creature comforts available such as-tv, vcr,microwave and barbeque.Don't feel like staying it's only a short walk to Restaurant's,Cafe's and beaches.

Situated 30 seconds off yamba's main road and two minute drive from beaches is heaven for any family or group check it out we've got. 
• Accommodation • Caravan & Camping sites - Ensuite & powered sites• 2 swimming pools (1 with spa) • Tidal salt water lagoon • Camp Kitchen• BBQ Areas • Children’s playgrounds • TV Room • Games Room • Internet Cafe
Feel like getting out  Yamba's at your doorstep,Win win situation.

UNIT 2
Check out this glorious view,doesn't get any better than this. Immaculate luxury unit that sleeps six people has two bathrooms and parking for two cars and a boat. 
Perfect for a few friends to getaway or spend it with loved one's the choice is yours.

Sandilands situated Yamba Hill has outstanding view overlooking one of Yamba's favorite surf beaches,Pippi Beach.

With two bedroom units bring the family or get your mates together for a surfing holiday.

Surf Motel is placed in a beautiful position overlooking Main beach, Lighthouse and Iluka.
Short walk to Pippi's Cafe or the Pacific hotel with the Restaurants and Cafe's  just down the hill.

The newest edition to Yamba is set up to cater for just about anything. It's smack bam in the middle of Yamba with it's multi share to family ensuites, It' own licenced bar and  cafe open for breakfast through to dinner. On the next floor you can enjoy our entertainment deck, float around our exclusive swimming pool perched above Yamba's main street. Step up on our roof deck if  feel like getting a tan with panoramic views of Yamba. We've got it all including – Undercover parking with lift, disabled rooms and bathroom facilities, bbq, laundry, communal kitchen, tv and reading, on site 24 hour managers, 24 internet cafe, free tea and coffee.
You can also step outside and explore Yamba's many beaches or cafe's, there's also fishing and for the surfers Angourie's only a 5 minute drive away.
Hours of operation:-
Reception: 8am to 9pm
Internet Café: 24 hours
Licensed Bar: 10am to 10pm
Café: 7am to 10pm

Units feature a  private balcony , with self contained kitchens in every room and some having spa's. This is the perfect holiday for families or couples with all Yamba's beauty at your doorstep.
